(754, 74, 'artist_bio', 'A graffiti writer and street artist, JABA’s complex and highly refined style is a synthesis of cubism, futurism and constructivism – where planes, angles and colours are pushed to the fore from his travels and experience as a concept artist for Lucasfilm Ltd and as a lecturer for Matte Painting, Environment & Character Design at Nanyang Polytechnic. JABA continues to practice on multidisciplinary levels and is currently an MA Fine Arts student at LASALLE College of the Arts.'),
