(803, 95, 'artist_bio', 'Shah Rizzal draws inspiration from the streets, where art presents itself as a communicable visual experience that relates to its surroundings and as a commentary of the present state. A self-taught aerosol painter prior to his formal arts training at LASALLE College of The Arts, he has completed various graffiti projects in Singapore through the years.'),
