(813, 98, 'description', 'Through his engagement with residents of Little India, Izzad Radzali Shah aims to transcribe oral-aural storytelling into visuals and symbols. Watch him paint this wall mural, titled Festival, live at 142 Dunlop Street.\r\n\r\nImage credits: Ng Wu Gang'),
