(837, 101, 'artist_bio', 'sobandwine is a Singaporean artist duo of Leow Wei Li and Dominic Khoo, who are in the fields of visual arts and music respectively. Their primary interest lies in expanding the interchangeable vocabulary of sounds and visuals. Their notable mural commissions include Nesuto, Botanist and Lunar Coffee Brewers.'),
