(848, 104, 'description', 'Inspired by Siyamala Bookstore’s 30-year history in Little India, Eunice Lim’s mural is a look into how information about heritage, histories, traditions and stories are discovered. Tiny hints are embedded into the mural by the artist, inviting visitors to embark on a journey of discovery about the bookstore and its occupant.\r\n\r\nImage credits: Ng Wu Gang'),
