(854, 104, 'artist_bio', 'Eunice Lim is a Singapore-based visual artist whose works utilizes systematic layers that parallels the forms of social conditionings, reflecting her interest in human relationships and cultural narratives. She has exhibited locally and internationally since graduating from LASALLE College of The Arts in 2014 with a BA (Hons) Fine Art.'),
