(886, 151, 'artist_bio', 'Kamini Ramachandran is a master storyteller with in-depth knowledge and respect for the oral tradition. As co-founder of MoonShadow Stories, she has played a vital role in reviving storytelling in Singapore through her passionate dedication to the artform. She has performed for previous editions of ARTWALK Little India and at various venues locally and internationally.'),
