(948, 117, 'description', 'All are welcome at ARTWALK Little India’s inaugural workout activity! Nithiya N. and a group of dedicated yoga practitioners will be conducting a free yoga session as the sun sets on Little India. Sunset Yoga invites participants to return to yoga as a physical and spiritual activity, by observing the bustling evening life of the precinct through mindfulness and key basic poses. This activity is suitable for beginners and all yoga enthusiasts. Comfortable yoga outfits are advised for all participants.'),
