(1760, 323, 'artist_bio', 'Dominic Tong (b. 1989) is a multidisciplinary artist based in Singapore. Having graduated with a Diploma in Film, Sound and Video from Ngee Ann Polytechnic in 2009. His works are predominantly in video although he enjoys experimenting with other mediums.\r\n\r\nIn 2015, he finished his undergraduate studies in LASALLE College of the Arts and was the recipient of The Winston Oh Travel Research Award 2015.'),
