(1847, 338, '_artist_name', 'field_5a4c9c7a6faa3'),
(1848, 338, 'artist_bio', 'This production is presented by LASALLE’s Diploma in Performance Programme. The programme trains performers to develop strategies and skills to interrogate the world and respond meaningfully with traditional, contemporary and experimental performance disciplines. Encompassing the significant rite of passage from apprentice to performer, this dynamic programme trains performers to recognise events that have the potential to be explored and developed into performance. Graduates go on to professional careers in theatre, film, television and live events.'),
