(1927, 352, 'artist_bio', 'Sanyaa Mehrotra\'s work is deeply personal and offers an intimate view of her reflections. The 21-year-old mixed media artist\'s practices arises from an interest in material exploration and her perspective of the world. She is constantly searching for knowledge and is passionately committed to daydreaming.\r\n\r\nSneha Mittal is a dreamer and sees the world as a place of fantasy. Her practice focuses on discovering the self and the idea of making the world a better place. As an artist, she feels responsible for spreading awareness and likes working for the good of society. She loves being surrounded by creativity.'),
