(1935, 353, 'description', 'Explore the ‘Sound of Dance’ with Nikita through Bharatanatyam. The workshop is designed to allow participants to experience dance as the source music, rather than as an accompaniment to music. It is suitable for beginners and all age 12 and above. Comfortable clothing is advised for all participants.'),
