(2055, 367, 'artist_bio', 'Kamini Ramachandran is a storyteller with a deep knowledge of the Asian oral tradition. With a focus on culture and heritage she is an experienced educator for museum-based learning and is known for her site-specific performances. Through MoonShadow Stories she pioneered storytelling for adult audiences and founded The Storytelling Centre Ltd to advance the art of storytelling through the Young Storytellers Mentorship Programme. She is also creative producer of StoryFest Singapore.'),
