(2071, 369, 'artist_bio', 'Soumee De is an Odissi dancer and co founder of ETHOS: exploring an Odissi Spirit, a community of odissi dancers that aims to inspire, propagate, develop and influence the spread of Odissi and related arts &amp; music disciplines across geographies, cultures and generations. Soumee has more than 30 years of classical dance experiences (in Kathak and Odissi) and currently teaches dance &amp; movement at Shantha Ratii SRI Academy and Temple of Fine Arts. She trains in Odissi under Guru Ratikant Mohapatra from Srjan, Bhubaneswar, India.'),
