(82, 1, '2017-12-13 22:01:48', '2017-12-13 14:01:48', '', 'Daily Delivery', 'Daily Delivery is JABA’s futuristic hyper-fictional vision of Little India’s Tiffin man. The Tiffin man’s mode of transport is intricately illustrated with ingenious recycling of old car models and an engine that depicts it hovering above the ground. Emphasising the idea of balancing the mix of tradition and modernisation, the mural is a tribute to the tiffin meal businesses that still exist to this day in the precinct, with the optimism that this traditional trade can grow sustainably alongside rapid developments in technology.', 'inherit', 'open', 'closed', '', 'proposalindia', '', '', '2018-01-03 16:46:13', '2018-01-03 08:46:13', '', 74, 'http://artwalklittleindia.sg/adm/wp-content/uploads/1.-JABA_Daily-Delivery_2018.jpg', 0, 'attachment', 'image/jpeg', 0),
