(172, 1, '2018-01-04 15:52:09', '2018-01-04 07:52:09', 'All are welcome at ARTWALK Little India’s inaugural workout activity! Nithiya N. and a group of dedicated yoga practitioners will be conducting a free yoga session as the sun sets on Little India. Sunset Yoga invites participants to return to yoga as a physical and spiritual activity, by observing the bustling evening life of the precinct through mindfulness and key basic poses. This activity is suitable for beginners and all yoga enthusiasts. Comfortable yoga outfits are advised for all participants.\n<!--more-->\n<strong>Location</strong>: POLI Site, Hindoo Road, TBC specific pin-drop\n<strong>Duration</strong>: 1 hour\n<strong>Dates and Timings</strong>: 18-20 and 25-27 January 2018, Thursdays-Saturdays, 6-7pm\n<strong>Level</strong>: Beginner-friendly\n<strong>Admission</strong>: <a href=\"https://artwalklittleindia2018.peatix.com/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Free via Registration on Peatix</a>\n\n<strong>About Free Yoga in Little India</strong>:\nFree Yoga in Little India is all about utilising community spaces in Little India in a fun new way, with the hope of bringing together the communities that inhabit and visit this culturally rich neighbourhood on a Sunday morning.', 'Sunset Yoga with Free Yoga in Little India', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '117-autosave-v1', '', '', '2018-01-04 15:52:09', '2018-01-04 07:52:09', '', 117, 'http://artwalklittleindia.sg/adm/2018/01/03/117-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
